# ===========================================
# ग्रामदर्पण - Environment Variables
# ===========================================
#
# Vercel + Neon Integration automatically sets these:
#   POSTGRES_PRISMA_URL          → Pooled connection (for Prisma Client)
#   POSTGRES_URL_NON_POOLING     → Direct connection (for Prisma CLI / migrations)
#   DATABASE_URL                 → Pooled connection (set by Neon integration)
#   DATABASE_URL_UNPOOLED        → Direct connection (set by Neon integration)
#
# You do NOT need to manually add these!
# Just click "Connect to Project" in Vercel's Neon integration.
#
# For LOCAL development with Neon PostgreSQL:
#   DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:pass@host/neondb?sslmode=require"
#   DATABASE_URL_UNPOOLED="postgresql://user:pass@direct-host/neondb?sslmode=require"
# ===========================================
